Package cst8284.asgmt3.roomScheduler

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Activity
    Activity contains the event's description and category of the RoomBooking object.
    ContactInfo
    Contact info contains the information of the customer of RoomBooking objects
    RoomBooking
    RoomBooking contains all information of a Booking.
    RoomScheduler
    RoomScheduler handle all events happen in the RoomBooking application.
    RoomSchedulerLauncher
    Room scheduler program implements an application that save information of room bookings and schedule them.
    SortRoomBookingsByCalendar
    SortRoomBookingByCalendar is used to compare object of type RoomBooking by Calendar
    TimeBlock
    TimeBlock contains the start time and end time of RoomBooking objects
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    BadRoomBookingException
    BadRoomBookingException class extends RuntimeException, handles exceptions thrown in the process of making a Booking.
